name: IN THE MOOD OF MALANG #4
description:
Always sad to remember this city.

Because Malang always brings longing. Longing about the atmosphere, the people, and the night.

Night in Malang has a magic of its own, the mist that presents the mystique melts with the light of the street lights. The buildings of the houses began to whisper, telling how long they had watched the hustle and bustle of people.
